      "_userAttributionCaveat": "None of these sources carry USERNAME. For user entity, requires two-step pivot: (1) resolve HOSTNAME/SRC_IP via concurrent Windows 4624 sessions, (2) filter network logs by those host/IP values. Status values below are for the user entity; for process entity all rows except firewall ones are 'ok'.",
